Duluth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota_Duluth\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Summer Beer Olympics, which was also held in three other breweries, was obviously in celebration of the 2024 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Games included a beer pong distance contest, a plank contest, and a \\\"Pass the Pint Relay\\\" in which competitors were judged on speed and not spilling a full pint of beer.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The breweries are perfect event hosts because it's a casual place to hang out,\\\" says Jappe.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It gets people of all ages, all levels out into the community supports local business like it's just such a great way for us to host events at fun places.\\\"\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more about the Minnesota Brewery Running Series and where they are headed next,check out their website.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1207, \"end\": 1216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\", \"score\": 0.5510436612679813, \"rank\": 0.8147061792029822, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_ice_hockey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You Might LikeLate Third Period Goal Lifts Hayward Girls Hockey Over Superior in Season OpenerUMD Men's Hoops Falls to Michigan Tech for 1st Loss of Season#5 UMD Women's Hockey Unable to Complete Comeback Against #3 Ohio StateNorthwestern Holds Off Stratford to Advance to State Title Game for First Time Since 1993    \\u00a9 2025 Fox21Online.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michigan_Wolv